title: Creamy Mushrooms & Potato Mash with Steamed Veggies & Herbs
description: Mushrooms and mashed potatoes, is there any more we need to say here? It’s a classic pairing of two wondrous flavours. They melt into each other as the longlife cream sauce spreads from the mushrooms to the steamed veggies. Simple and delicious.

